  <summary>9/25/1997--Introduced.
Amends the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 1997 to apply to each military separation occurring after December 31, 1993, an amendment which provides that amounts required for the payment of Federal income tax shall be subtracted from military retired pay for purposes of determining an individual's offset in concurrent veterans' disability compensation.</summary>
